      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INTREPID EAGLE (2) jumped well to win over the 630m at this track two runs back then prominent throughout when finishing third at this track last start. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from eight starts. Top prospect. ASHBY GNOCCHI (1) showed strong pace early from the inside rail and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fourth over 630m this track in 37.14. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. SNEAKY TYCOON (4) was below best at his last start when 8th at Gosford following a second place finish (35.22) there two back. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ZIPPING HOPKINS (7) was strongly fancied last time but ran below expectations when sixth (37.34), beaten 6 lengths. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings seven times from nine attempts.",
